aggr(data)

data_clean <- data %>% drop_na()
aggr(data_clean)

head(data_clean_long)
Sales_Year<-data_clean %>% group_by(Year) %>% summarise(Global_Sales_Year = sum(Global_Sales), 
                                                        Other_Sales_Year = sum(Other_Sales),
                                                        Japan_Sales_Year = sum(JP_Sales),
                                                        NorthAmerica_Sales_Year = sum(NA_Sales),
                                                        Europe_Sales_Year = sum(EU_Sales))
head(Sales_Year)
SalesByYear<- Sales_Year %>% ggplot() +
    geom_line(mapping=aes(x=Year, y=Global_Sales_Year, col="Global")) +
    geom_line(mapping=aes(x=Year,y=Other_Sales_Year, col="Other"))+
    geom_line(mapping=aes(x=Year,y=Japan_Sales_Year, col="Japan"))+
    geom_line(mapping=aes(x=Year,y=NorthAmerica_Sales_Year, col="NorthAmerica"))+
    geom_line(mapping=aes(x=Year,y=Europe_Sales_Year, col="Europe"))+
    scale_color_manual(name="Region", values=c("Global"="deeppink3","Other"="coral2","Japan"="darkolivegreen",
                                "NorthAmerica"="darkcyan", "Europe"="darkseagreen"))+
   ggtitle("Sold Games by Region") +
    ylab("Sold Games (in million copies)")+
    theme_bw() + 
      theme(
    plot.title = element_text(face = "bold", size = 12, hjust = 0.5),
          axis.text = element_text(size = 9),
    legend.background = element_rect(fill = "white", size = 4, colour = "white"),
    #legend.justification = c(0, 1),
    legend.position = c(0.125, 0.75),
    axis.ticks = element_line(colour = "grey70", size = 0.2),
    panel.grid.major = element_line(colour = "grey70", size = 0.2),
    panel.grid.minor = element_blank()
      )+
      transition_reveal(Year)
animate(SalesByYear, res = 69)
anim_save("SalesByYear.gif", animation = last_animation(), path = NULL)
include_graphics("SalesByYear.gif")

PlatformByYear <- data_clean_long %>% filter(Sales_Type!="Global_Sales")  %>%
    ggplot(aes(fill=Sales_Type, x=Platform, y=Sales_Region))+
    geom_bar(position="stack", stat="identity") + 
        ggtitle("Sales by Region and Platform") +
        ylab("Sales (in million copies) by Region")+
        xlab("Type of Platform")+
        coord_flip()+
    theme_bw() + 
      theme(
        plot.title = element_text(face = "bold", size = 12, hjust = 0.5),
        axis.text = element_text(size = 9),
        axis.ticks = element_line(colour = "grey70", size = 0.2),
        panel.grid.major = element_line(colour = "grey70", size = 0.2),
        panel.grid.minor = element_blank()
          ) +
    transition_time(Year) +
      labs(subtitle = "Year: {frame_time}") 
animate(PlatformByYear, nframes=40,duration=80, res = 69)
anim_save("PlatformByYear.gif", animation = last_animation(), path = NULL)
knitr::include_graphics("PlatformByYear.gif")
